second position again with a 4-1 win-loss record.
</P>
<P>
Earlier today, Indonesia overpowered winless Malaysia 15-6,
15-4, 15-7 to finish third with a 3-2 record.
</P>
<P>
Vietnam took fourth place, beating the Philippines into fifth
with a 15-13, 15-5, 15-11 win. 
